edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner

Class LeisureEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.Event
      • edu.subram43purdue.travelplanner.LeisureEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class LeisureEvent
extends Event
    This class represents a Leisure Event of a vacation, which is one of the two subclasses of Event, and contains five fields, three of which are inherited from the Event class (name, date, and time). The two extra fields are event location and event note, which are traits specific to a leisure event
